reviews.text: Small restaurant with heart. Quite a variety of choices, from Hainan Chicken, fried rice, Chinese style scramble eggs, to curry dishes, pan fried minced pork with preserved veggie. Good quality cheap option in this area, but only have limited seats, so better be there early, or choose the take away option.
Quick lunch
成日食都有新菜式，即叫即整，係要預時間約10至20分鐘等候，不過非常值得去等。
路過唔好錯過.........惹味爽滑口水🐔。
店雖小，但出品美味，價錢也不貴，值得再來。由於是小店，最好是午飯時間後及秋冬天氣較好
